2019 Population data

Source: R/pop_data.R
pop_data.Rd

A dataset containing 2019 population data for 221 countries.

pop_data

Format

a tibble with 221 observations and 2 variables:

  • country: Country name

  • population: Population data for 2019

Source

World Bank

Examples

pop_data
